## Summary
The Experiment iOS SDK documentation provides comprehensive guidance for implementing client-side feature flags and experiments in iOS applications, covering installation via CocoaPods or Swift Package Manager, initialization with Amplitude Analytics or third-party providers, variant fetching, exposure tracking, and local/remote evaluation capabilities.

